53
00:02:56.118 --> 00:02:58.427
offers is

54
00:02:59.435 --> 00:03:01.871
the fulfillment of our humanness,

55
00:03:02.038 --> 00:03:06.006
not something that marginalizes

56
00:03:06.006 --> 00:03:09.717
our humanness or disregards it, but

57
00:03:09.717 --> 00:03:13.461
for Rumi and for all sufis and also for

58
00:03:13.461 --> 00:03:14.805
the prophet Mohammad,

59
00:03:14.805 --> 00:03:19.805
becoming fully human in cooperation with the divine

60
00:03:21.727 --> 00:03:25.199
while living an integrated

61
00:03:25.812 --> 00:03:28.921
useful, practical life.

62
00:03:31.663 --> 00:03:33.753
These are the conditions in which

63
00:03:34.110 --> 00:03:34.914
our

64
00:03:36.499 --> 00:03:39.319
greatest spirituality can be reached.

65
00:03:39.699 --> 00:03:42.988
Without sacrificing the

66
00:03:43.742 --> 00:03:47.038
highest dimensions of human

67
00:03:47.038 --> 00:03:49.005
spiritual attainment.

68
00:03:49.086 --> 00:03:53.090
In other words, without sacrificing

69
00:03:53.490 --> 00:03:57.666
the experience of oneness

