156
00:08:49.941 --> 00:08:54.089
a possibility, as a yearning for something

157
00:08:54.089 --> 00:08:58.169
extraordinarily pure and beautiful.

158
00:08:58.228 --> 00:09:00.968
This is innate in our souls,

159
00:09:00.968 --> 00:09:03.081
