00:29:18.817 --> 00:29:22.859
He has a sober teaching and a systematic teaching,

532
00:29:22.859 --> 00:29:27.859
and a great spiritual psychology that's very practical

533
00:29:28.737 --> 00:29:29.356
as well.

534
00:29:29.356 --> 00:29:30.966
<v Woman>It seems the West has more or less</v>

