00:29:38.411 --> 00:29:39.969
embraced, but you know that's a wonderful

539
00:29:39.969 --> 00:29:40.821
starting place.

540
00:29:40.821 --> 00:29:41.376
<v ->It's a beginning.</v>

541
00:29:41.376 --> 00:29:42.879
<v Woman>It's a wonderful beginning.</v>

542
00:29:42.879 --> 00:29:45.178
<v ->And that ecstasy and that bliss,</v>

